     \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you want to use this tracking system, you must first create a \u003ca href=\"https://app.grammarly.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGrammarly account\u003c/a\u003e. The great thing about this AI app is it’s free, so you don’t have to spend a dime just to prove that you did your own work. When you have your account, you must install \u003ca href=\"https://www.grammarly.com/browser/chrome\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGrammarly for Chrome\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"https://www.grammarly.com/browser/edge\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGrammarly for Microsoft Edge\u003c/a\u003e (depending on your preferred browser) if you’re writing on Google Docs. But if you prefer working on Microsoft Word, you must install \u003ca href=\"https://www.grammarly.com/desktop\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGrammarly for Desktop\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"917f-4e06-b0653018dd41\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/best-free-ai-apps/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A happy AI robot above a smartphone screen, with icons of some AI apps in the background.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-happy-ai-robot-above-a-smartphone-screen-with-icons-of-some-ai-apps-in-the-background.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/best-free-ai-apps/\" title=\"8 Free AI Apps You’re Not Using (But Should Be)\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t8 Free AI Apps You’re Not Using (But Should Be)\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eUse AI to edit text, create images, and learn a language—without paying a cent. \u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen you’ve installed the needed apps and logged into your account, a pop-up inviting you to try the Authorship should appear. After pressing \u003cstrong\u003eOK \u003c/strong\u003eor closing the window, a small green thumbprint icon should appear in the lower-left corner of your screen. Click on it to expand the Authorship window, and then press \u003cstrong\u003eTrack writing activity\u003c/strong\u003e so that it will start tracking the document you’re working on.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Grammarly Authorship pop-up window\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/grammarly-authorship-pop-up-window.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen you’re done working, you can then press the green thumbprint icon again to reveal your options and press \u003cstrong\u003eSee report\u003c/strong\u003e. A browser window will then open to show the statistics for that file, at least for the current session.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"it-rsquo-s-not-perfect-but-it-rsquo-s-a-start\"\u003e\n                        It’s Not Perfect, but It’s a Start\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGrammarly’s Authorship feature is a great way to help prove that you’re not cheating on the paper you’re writing on. However, it has a few drawbacks. For example, it only tracks the current session of a particular document. So, if you decide to close the file and come back to it later, the Authorship report will mark the existing text in the file with ‘Origin unknown’.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Losing tracking progress on Grammarly Authorship after restarting a file\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/losing-tracking-progress-on-grammarly-authorship-after-restarting-a-file.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can also open an AI app on another device or window, and then you can just retype it into your document. If you do that, Authorship will report it as ‘100% Typed by a human’ — even though it’s AI-generated work.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAnyone with intent can and will circumvent tools that protect against plagiarism and the use of AI. However, this is much better than \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/ai-checkers-are-useless-examples-prove-why/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAI checkers, which we’ve already proven are useless in detecting AI-written content\u003c/a\u003e. There’s even some talk that these are negatively biased against non-native English speakers and writers.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAuthorship can help give educators confidence that the work their students are submitting is original. But if a teacher has second thoughts about the originality of the work someone handed in, the only way to know for sure is to have the student present it to them in person.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n                            \n    \n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
